102
00:03:40,068 --> 00:03:41,8
(gasps)

103
00:03:44,010 --> 00:03:45,0
(coughing)

104
00:03:47,081 --> 00:03:49,3
Hey.

105
00:03:49,052 --> 00:03:50,4
